{"tid":2204534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【垃圾黨鐵又壞】港鐵彩虹站附近信號故障　九龍塘至觀塘列車服務暫停","createTime":"2020-09-16T06:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T08:58:19.000Z","uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"277935b5791e8905fb376b9491e678dd23a84679","tid":2204534,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1549907_2_20200916142658.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1549907_2_20200916142658.jpg&h=23bcaca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n列車服務維持來回黃埔站至九龍塘站，及觀塘站至調景嶺站，每10分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，觀塘綫彩虹站附近有信號故障，九龍塘站至觀塘站之間的列車服務暫停。<br />\n<br />\n列車服務維持來回黃埔站至九龍塘站，及觀塘站至調景嶺站，每10分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵人員已進入路軌範圍，進行復修工作，呼籲乘客為行程預留充裕乘車時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵正安排免費接駁巴士，行走九龍塘至觀塘站，乘客請考慮使用其他鐵路綫或公共交通工具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549907-20200916.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549907-20200916.htm&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=6dcf0694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549907-20200916.htm&h=25589866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549907-20200916.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2cdb0daf221819e798e29bb65054885804f7d7e1","tid":2204534,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦"},{"pid":"54ebcb1a5360820114c4fa2b7203de0745569a74","tid":2204534,"uid":8932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"執7左佢啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"612761138bc342200278262679aa56213f4c6202","tid":2204534,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"屌你idle time都可以壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882